      "index": 1,
      "text": "He chose the callsign after the coup, Sumire, because of the lucky shot he fired that killed [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMastiff],Raju Mastiff]] in the cockpit of his <i>Centurion</i>.\n\nAs a reward, Director [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSantiagoEspinosa],Espinosa]] promoted Guardsman Korais to an officer in the [[DM.Factions[faction_AuriganDirectorate],Directorate]]'s armed forces.\n",
