    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c6d22a25358bdc8e1db23f1"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "All our 'Mechs were sabotaged, so that shot was also an easy one, but from what I remember about Korais, calling himself a 'legend' sounds like quite a bloated achievement.",
