      "text": "This is Korais... he is now a captain in the Directorate but Director Espinosa never really trusted him after the coup, so he wasn't assigned to hunt the company or Lady Arano.\n\nHis betrayal also caused the death of Commander [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMarkhamsMarauders],Markham]] after he refused Director Espinosa's order to surrender, and instead tried to rescue Kamea.",
